|                                                                                  |
| 9. Run complete algorithm (Calibration,create video)                             |
| 10. Run complete algorithm - Dynamic calibration -> custom white & yellow filters|
| 11. Run complete algorithm - Dynamic calibration -> with all filters in stack    |
